high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the wall, hang a right, go to the counter across the room.
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter.
Move to right to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, turn the water on to rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Go to the right to the wall, hang a right, go forward, turn around and face the cupboard.
Put the spoon in the rightmost cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk around the island and go to the kitchen counter to the left of the sink.
Grab a spoon from the counter.
Go to the sink on the right.
Place the spoon in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Walk to the kitchen cabinet on the right.
Put the spoon in the bottom-right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Wash a spoon and put it away.

high_descs: Go left and then to the right and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the spoon up from the counter.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the spoon up again.
Go to the right and face the lower cabinet to the right of the dishwasher.
Put the spoon in the lower cabinet to the right of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the cabinet.
